<ul>
  <li>Thereâ€™s a â€˜Compare itemsâ€™ function that I canâ€™t figure out how to use at all.</li>
  <li>It always says â€˜Welcome -â€˜ (My name <em>IS</em> filled out in account information).</li>
  <li>It consistently labels my cart with the wrong number of items (This is often because a â€˜freebieâ€™ thatâ€™s added, that I already own, but not shown in all windows).</li>
