<p>Overall, the process of buying the product seems amateurish to me. Itâ€™s not <em>difficult</em> to purchase the product, but itâ€™s not nearly as slick as it could be. When you depend on income from affordable software, then impulse purchases should be easy and not half a dozen extra clicks.</p>

